parts:
# Kovan Area Tuition Center Rental Options

Below are several **commercial rental listings in the Kovan area** that meet your criteria (≈250–350 sq ft, under S$5k/month, near MRT). Each option includes key details like size, price, proximity to MRT, property type/features, and available contact or listing info for follow-up.

## Option 1: Block 204 Hougang Street 21 (Kovan)  
- **Size & Rent:** ~300 sq ft | S$1,800 per month (≈S$6.00 psf)【19†L74-L77】.  
- **Distance to MRT:** ~200 m (3–4 min walk) to **NE13 Kovan MRT**【19†L108-L115】 (right next to Heartland Mall).  
- **Property Type/Features:** HDB commercial **office space** on Hougang St 21, partitioned into an office room plus open area. Comes with air-conditioning, file cabinets, and an **attached toilet**【19†L108-L115】. The unit is on a convenient ground-floor block very close to eateries and amenities.  
- **Suitable Use:** Landlord explicitly notes it’s *“suitable for tuition & educational usage”*【19†L108-L115】. (Also ideal for small startups or other businesses.)  
- **Contact/Listing:** Listed by agent Larry Chua – see SRX Commercial listing ID 101328371【19†L94-L102】【19†L108-L115】 for photos and details (CEA Reg. R007359A, Tel: 8138 XXXX).

## Option 2: Upper Serangoon Shopping Centre (756 Upper Serangoon Rd)  
- **Size & Rent:** ~312 sq ft | **Starting from** S$1,500 per month【26†L42-L50】 (negotiable; ~S$4.80 psf).  
- **Distance to MRT:** ≈900 m (11 min walk) to **NE12 Serangoon MRT**【26†L53-L56】, and also a short bus ride or ~5 min drive from Kovan MRT (NE13)【26†L119-L125】.  
- **Property Type/Features:** **Retail shop unit** in an established 3-story shopping mall (strata-titled). It’s a bare unit but *“aircon supply [during] mall’s operating hours”* is **included** in rent【26†L101-L108】. Upper Serangoon SC is an older mall, but offers *low-cost space* suitable for a small office or classroom setup. **No GST** on rent (owner not GST-registered)【26†L103-L110】, and landlord is open to 1-2 year lease terms【26†L103-L110】.  
- **Suitable Use:** Described as a *“good size…for small office and retail”*【26†L101-L108】. A tuition centre could operate here (subject to any necessary change-of-use approvals) given the commercial zoning. Being within a mall means foot traffic from neighboring shops and amenities (eateries, etc.) is a plus【26†L117-L125】.  
- **Contact/Listing:** Listed on PropertyGuru by agent Bryan Cheng – refer to CommercialGuru Listing ID 25542652【26†L97-L105】【26†L113-L121】 for details. (You may contact the agent via the listing page; number is partially masked as 8***** in the ad.)

## Option 3: The Promenade @ Pelikat (183 Jalan Pelikat)  
- **Size & Rent:** ~244 sq ft | S$1,400 per month【40†L64-L72】 (about S$5.74 psf). *Note:* 244 sq ft is just below your 250 sq ft preference, but this unit is very close to the target size.  
- **Distance to MRT:** ~810 m (10 min walk) to **NE13 Kovan MRT**【40†L74-L80】. (Located near Yio Chu Kang Road/Jalan Pelikat junction – in the Kovan/Hougang vicinity.)  
- **Property Type/Features:** **Mall shop unit** in *The Promenade @ Pelikat*, a modern mixed development (completed 2016)【40†L96-L100】. The unit is **partially fitted** (basic flooring/ceiling done)【40†L94-L100】 and ready for move-in. It’s within a small shopping arcade frequented by residents of the building and neighborhood. The development is relatively new, so the facilities are modern and well-maintained.  
- **Suitable Use:** Good for a small retail storefront or office; a tuition centre could be set up as a small classroom here (several education/enrichment centers already operate in similar HDB malls and small commercial units). Being in a mall setting, it provides a professional space for students/parents. (Do ensure the unit’s usage category allows “Education/Training Centre” – typically permissible in commercial shop spaces.)  
- **Contact/Listing:** Listed by agent Joanne Tan Siew May (Huttons Asia) – see CommercialGuru Listing ID 25475951【40†L72-L80】【40†L94-L100】 for photos and contact. (CEA Reg. R055037C; agent’s tel. available via the listing page or inquiry form.)

## Option 4: Kensington Square (2 Jalan Lokam) – *Bartley* area  
- **Size & Rent:** ~297 sq ft | S$1,999 per month【44†L79-L87】 (~S$6.73 psf; landlord looking for offers around $2k).  
- **Distance to MRT:** ~470–500 m to **CC12 Bartley MRT** on the Circle Line (approx. 7–8 minutes’ walk)【48†L41-L44】. *Note:* This site is about 1.6 km from Kovan MRT (a ~5-minute drive or bus ride), as it’s located toward the Bartley/Upper Paya Lebar side of District 19.  
- **Property Type/Features:** **Retail shop unit** in *Kensington Square*, a mixed development (ground-floor retail shops with condos above) completed in 2017. This is a **ground-floor shop** for rent (available immediately)【44†L79-L87】, ideal for a small business. The development has a modern “neighborhood mall” concept with a handful of shops and eateries serving the condo and nearby landed estate – providing some walk-in traffic.  
- **Suitable Use:** The landlord markets it as an *“ideal unit, ideal location”* for someone looking to start a shop【44†L101-L105】. It can accommodate a small tuition or enrichment centre – you’d get a self-contained shop space in a new development, with visibility to residents in the area. Being near Bartley MRT also makes it accessible. (As always, confirm usage approvals for running a tuition center, but commercial zoning should allow it.)  
- **Contact/Listing:** Listed by agent Eileen Leong (ERA) – see SRX listing ID 89914231【44†L79-L87】【44†L95-L103】 for details and contact. (Tel: 9274 XXXX on listing; you can reach out via the listing’s “Enquire Now” or WhatsApp link.)

### Sources

Each option above is based on current property listings from major portals (PropertyGuru/CommercialGuru, SRX, etc.) and includes information verified from those listings. Refer to the cited sources for more details and up-to-date availability: **Block 204 Hougang St21 Office**【19†L94-L102】【19†L108-L115】, **Upper Serangoon Shopping Ctr Listing**【26†L101-L109】【26†L117-L125】, **The Promenade @ Pelikat Listing**【40†L72-L80】【40†L94-L100】, **Kensington Square Shop Listing**【44†L79-L87】【48†L41-L44】. Each citation link will take you to the respective listing or property page for contact information and additional photos.
